Commercial




Commercial
Pexco’s plastic solutions for Commercial market segments typically fulfill high-volume product applications involving everyday retail or consumer utility.




 

 

 







Capabilities
Shaping your vision

In this market, both OEM and distributor customers benefit from innovation with conventional product concepts and designs which often expect the high-throughput manufacturing speed, capacity and experience that Pexco provides. Learn More >



Fence
Enjoy your privacy

For over 40 years, Pexco’s PDS® and PVT® branded fence products have been changing the look of chain link fence systems.  The PDS® product line is a result of numerous slat designs, functions, patents and personnel, all of which have helped Pexco pioneer chain-link enhancement over decades.



Consumer
Everyday items








Pexco is a leading presence in the Consumer Products industry, serving companies across multiple sub-sectors including Writing Instruments,Food & Beverage, Personal Care & Safety, and Household Products.



Team Up
Interested in working with Pexco?








When you partner with Pexco, you get the benefits of a sophisticated plastics processor with locations across the United States and Mexico. You also gain from a culture that is nimble and customer focused. Yes, we’re bigger than most other specialty plastic companies, but we are devoted to the kind of individual approach to business that underlies years of successful plastics solutions for customers.





















 




                Medical Grade Plastics Manufacturer - Medical Thermoplastic Fabrication | PEXCO
        


























