Medical Brochure
For over 50 years, Pexco products have been recognized as leading and innovating solutions for the medical plastics industry.  As an FDA registered contract manufacturer with ability to do medical tubing, profile extrusion, CNC machining, and specialty injection molding, our focus on quality is why customers look to Pexco to meet their detailed product needs.




Medical Capabilities
A Powerful Combination








Pexco’s capabilities include medical tubing extrusion; injection molding; plastic profile extrusion; assembly, packaging, and sterilization management services; and more.
