Traffic





Traffic Safety Products
Pexco Davidson Traffic Control Products is an innovative plastics manufacturer of traffic safety products and solutions.  Committed to innovation and performance, Pexco is dedicated to "creating products to save lives."




 

 

 

 

 

 

 

 

 

 







Traffic Safety Products >

With multiple production and distribution facilities throughout the U.S. and abroad, we are able to serve our customers locally while reducing costs with high quality products.
 

Bollards and Channelizer Posts
Posts for Separated Bike Lanes
Lane Separator Curb Systems
Roadside Delineator Posts
Jersey Barrier Reflectors
Guardrail Reflectors
Specialty Reflectors
Snow Poles & Posts
Pavement Markers
Parking and Facility Management
Pedestrian Safety Products
Barricade Products
Support Products



Traffic Applications >
Use our filtered table to find the exact product you need by application.  Learn more >>
 


Ultra-High Performance City Post SM Surface Mount








 Meet the newest addition to the City Post family!  In recent testing, the City Post SM Surface Mount set new standards for bolt-down channelizers in durability, ultra-high impact resistance, and superior strength.  The City Post SM remains flexible, even at extremely high and low temperatures, and returns to a full upright position even after 100 impacts at 60 mph (100 km/h).  Learn more >





Contact the Traffic Sales Team








Pexco's Traffic team is here to serve the customer by location.  Learn More >





