Future Website of Pexco Aerospace













Pexco Aerospace is a leading manufacturer of aircraft related components and assemblies for Commercial Aerospace applications. Our highly engineered solutions have been utilized on thousands of programs and critical applications including many of today’s most innovative and groundbreaking programs such as the Boeing 787.
We bring 30+ years of experience manufacturing and supplying aerospace plastic components to OEMs and distributors.






 





 







 







 







 





 







