FedEx Case Study








 Pexco’s PDS® Fence products can be supplied in your specific custom colors, defining your brand at your facility or location – utilizing existing chain link fence or a new installation.
Learn More >



PVT® Retail  Fence Products >

Like our PDS® Fence slats, our PVT® Fence slats provide the same privacy and security, but are available through leading retail home centers in the U.S.


Landscape Edging Products >

Pexco's landscape edging products are used to create a clean perimeter or border around a garden or floral area. They are easy to install and help with weed control. These products are now available through leading retail home center stores throughout the U.S.




